Poor customer service! Many times I arrive home to find something missing from my order. I recently took the time to drive back to get a refund for my missing items from 2 receipts, and was made to feel like I was the problem for expecting to get what I ordered and paid for. The manager sarcastically told me they were only doing their best. I was offered nothing, I had to ask for a refund of missing items. I remember when Raisin Cane had excellent customer service. I easily could have left happy if the manager had handled the situation differently. This location is poorly managed. Stay in line and check your order.
